{"tid":961431,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"震撼74億人　艾利臣呢腳超癲","createTime":"2018-12-30T06:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T07:27:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e35dfbb35382495842bde4ce2df2e6cbe1cca26e","tid":961431,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"利物浦依家強勢打爆全英超，門將艾利臣比加來投令成條防線「升呢」，呢位巴西國腳救波、腳法出色就全世界都知，「紅軍」今場對阿仙奴嘅第4個入波，艾利臣比加唔單止係攻勢發起者，佢嘅大局觀同精準超級長傳更加睇到球迷O晒咀！ <br />\n<br />\n當時上半場就快完結，阿仙奴一次攻勢結束後，艾利臣比加拎住個波望兩望，突然車身狂抽個波去右邊，恰到好處畀落中場線空晒嘅羅拔圖法明奴隻腳度，造就呢次突擊機會，果然由穆罕默德沙拿博到12碼兼射入，賽後大批網民狂讚艾利臣比加派牌超掂，有粉絲直頭話以為沙比阿朗素返咗嚟利物浦添呀！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181230/mobile/bkn-20181230100124976-1230_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181230%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181230100124976-1230_00882_001.html&d=64hfh1fhp%2Fb782P9UO5lbS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8155bd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181230/mobile/bkn-20181230100124976-1230_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb21b7bee06b130ed118058ea95e6725796339f4","tid":961431,"uid":34858,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"74億人都撐利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3639f1d2a1dffcda9721fe9af641b5a503ea580d","tid":961431,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb21b7bee06b130ed118058ea95e6725796339f4","tid":961431,"uid":34858,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"74億人都撐利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"637ca02cd465f77121f60339b6125bb3eb730132","tid":961431,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cb21b7bee06b130ed118058ea95e6725796339f4","tid":961431,"uid":34858,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T06:25:2